{"tid":1692493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅智光稱有公務員參加示威不代表政府內部有問題","createTime":"2019-11-04T06:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T06:10:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7aa836953ed839b3248d53aef2930b9db39b352f","tid":1692493,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"公務員事務局局羅智光表示，局方非常關注有公務員在示威中被捕，會依法跟進，而政府上下會一同止暴制亂。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，有公務員參加示威，不代表政府內部有問題，整體公務員仍盡忠職守。<br />\n<br />\n羅智光希望立法會財委會盡快通過公務員薪酬調整建議，對有議員要求將警務人員加薪從公務員加薪項目抽出處理，他表示，有關建議偏離既定機制，並不合理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489981-20191104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489981-20191104.htm&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfp2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=e535ec31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489981-20191104.htm&h=127a323a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489981-20191104.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ccec3078a555c32b312429a41f7238cb8ed83e8e","tid":1692493,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"11月2同11月3之後，整理左少少資訊，得閒可以入黎一齊傾下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692149</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}